' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/aa779698f3eed4f3f91c5cda45e8c90c19242f262143b72758983c72b90bd524?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/keyurgajera/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ramjipatel <small>(keyurgajera)</small></a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng 4 2, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thanks team for great support, help in issue troubleshooting and clear and friendly communication!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/eligore/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/397759d4232847514e837da51fd6000651b797ad0933d5912828607e408eb67b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/397759d4232847514e837da51fd6000651b797ad0933d5912828607e408eb67b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/eligore/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">eligore</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng 3 31, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div clas